race.comment: DANCING JUICE (2) was well backed to start $3.90 last start at Geelong in what looks a key form reference. He got back there in a bit of a dash home there but should relish getting to 1980m now and can turn the tables on a few rivals. BARRINGTON MANOR (9) and LAYBUY (8) both come through the same race. BARRINGTON MANOR boxed on for second, beaten a length by LAYBUY there. LAYBUY was first up there so it's fair to assume improvement but he is a 9yo and we'd like to see him do it again. PARABELLUM (12) can mix her form but the win two back was dominant at Wangaratta and she can prove hard to hold out. DASHING DONKEY (10) should get a lovely run on speed which will suit.
